{
  "code": "001_PRO003C",
  "route": "001",
  "locale": "cn",
  "beats": [
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_001",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_001.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「早上好。今天因为学生会的工作所以起得早。」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_002",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_002.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「田径部加油哦。」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_003",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_003.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「翼，你今天有社团活动吗？会晚回来吗？」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_004",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_004.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「今天因为学生会的工作可能会晚回来。」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_005",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_005.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「哎呀，你等着我吗？」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_006",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_006.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「抱歉让你久等了。我晚了。」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_007",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_007.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「那我们一起回去吧。」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_008",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_008.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「你找我有什么事吗？」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_009",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_009.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「稍微有点事要去找老师……」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_010",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_010.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「放学后……嗯，知道了……」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_011",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_011.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「又，又要等吗！？呜呜，怎么……」"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "望月真琴",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MAKO_001_PRO003C_012",
        "file": "voice/mako_001_pro003C_012.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「是这样啊……知道了……」"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bgm": {
    "track": "M01",
    "file": "bgm/M01.ogg"
  }
}
